snippet.title: ThinkBigAnimation
snippet.description:
ThinkBigAnimation creates motivational content by bridging complex concepts from various fields to understand how they can actually be applied in life. 

From philosophy, psychology, mythology, spirituality, architecture, literature, modern media, just about any field involving the human psyche is on our radar. We investigate how all these fields influence our behavior and how they can inspire personal growth in all aspects of life – from dating, work, productivity, spirituality, EVERYTHING.
